{"tid":1295301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北俊：修例爭議後特首或想辭職，兩問責官員換人不難，點名張宇人，湯家驊，葉劉淑儀辭職","createTime":"2019-07-08T03:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T04:27:34.000Z","uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fcfe462bea40cb2486bda78571fd0152e4dec79e","tid":1295301,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"自由黨榮譽主席田北俊表示，在反對修訂《逃犯條例》事件後，感覺行政長官林鄭月娥想辭職，因為再做下去只會日日被人指責，民望評分比前特首梁振英還低，以前做任何事都是第一，現時在市民心中「排第尾」，相信對她的打擊很大，但估計林鄭月娥要繼續「頂下去」完成手尾，都是正確。<br />\n<br />\n至於律政司司長鄭若驊及保安局局長李家超的去留，田北俊出席一個電台節目時說，相信要填補兩人的空缺並不難，例如可由即將退休的警務處處長盧偉聰接任保安局局長。<br />\n<br />\n不過田北俊提到，司長局是由中央任命，反而行政會議成員是由特首任命，建議可重組行會，田北俊建議黨主席張宇人辭去行會成員之外，點名另外兩名行會成員辭職，包括本身是資深大律師的湯家驊及新民黨主席葉劉淑儀，他認為湯家驊未能掌握民意，提供錯誤意見給特首，而葉劉淑儀就極力支持修例。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467156-20190708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467156-20190708.htm&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=1337d275\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467156-20190708.htm&h=99ea6100\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467156-20190708.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a74da2eb6413b78367e5e191233b31cd41890bb4","tid":1295301,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aae08765bb698c680934699b3678b50b164a36a","tid":1295301,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"他認為湯家驊未能掌握民意，提供錯誤意見給特首<br />\n<br />\n邊樣先？送中條例？"},{"pid":"9d116f8cf27e4613e24a6bd385062b4a24224d55","tid":1295301,"uid":60524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:12:57.000Z","msg":"掃把頭難得入到行會 田少又追擊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08110ed0cd2358464d8f6385a72790eec2b6960","tid":1295301,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d116f8cf27e4613e24a6bd385062b4a24224d55","tid":1295301,"uid":60524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:12:57.000Z","msg":"掃把頭難得入到行會 田少又追擊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a6c44187f39295cc4d870efc48357e7c8c7b98","tid":1295301,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aae08765bb698c680934699b3678b50b164a36a","tid":1295301,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"他認為湯家驊未能掌握民意，提供錯誤意見給特首<br />\n<br />\n邊樣先？送中條例？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"衰11"}]}